<figcaption id="mntl-figure-caption_1-0" class="comp mntl-figure-caption text-utility-100 figure-article-caption"> <span class="figure-article-caption-owner">Meredith Food Studios</span>
</figcaption></figure>
<span class="heading-toc" id="toc-the-secret-to-super-moist-banana-bread"></span><h2 id="mntl-sc-block_9-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block allrecipes-sc-block-heading mntl-sc-block-heading"> <span class="mntl-sc-block-heading__text text-title-300"> The Secret to Super Moist Banana Bread </span> </h2>
<p id="mntl-sc-block_10-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html"> This banana bread is super moist thanks to butter, eggs, and brown sugar (which adds more moisture than white sugar). Plus, ripe mashed bananas have plenty of moisture on their own. Bake the bread until just done to prevent it drying out, and wrap the cooled loaf tightly in plastic wrap or foil to lock in moisture.
</p>
<div id="mntl-sc-block_11-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div>
<div id="mntl-sc-block_12-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block allrecipes-sc-block-featuredlink mm-myrecipes-sc-featured-link mntl-sc-block-universal-featured-link mntl-sc-block-universal-featured-link--related"><a
href="https://www.allrecipes.com/longform/best-banana-bread-review/"
rel="nocaes"
id="mntl-sc-block-universal-featured-link__link_1-0"
class="mntl-sc-block-universal-featured-link__link mntl-text-link text-utility-300 global-link"
data-tracking-container="true"
data-tracking-id="featured-link"
><span class="link__wrapper">I Tried Our 5 Most Popular Banana Bread Recipes and There Was One Clear Winner</span></a>
</div>
<div id="mntl-sc-block_13-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div>
<figure id="mntl-sc-block_14-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block allrecipes-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block-image--no-theme no-theme figure-square figure-high-res"> <div class="figure-media">
<div class="img-placeholder" style="padding-bottom:80.0%;">
<img
