<LI id="mntl-sc-block_52-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup mntl-sc-block-group--LI">
<p id="mntl-sc-block_53-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html"> Bake in the preheated oven until a toothpick inserted into the center comes out clean, about 60 minutes.
</p>
