<LI id="mntl-sc-block_57-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup mntl-sc-block-group--LI">
<p id="mntl-sc-block_58-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html"> Let bread cool in pan for 10 minutes, then turn out onto a wire rack to cool completely.
</p>
