<div id="ugc-review__text_1-0" class="comp ugc-review__text mntl-text-block">To make it a little more diabetic friendly I swapped half the flour with whole wheat, and half the banana with plantain. I also reduced the sugar. I used half the batter for banana bread donuts.</div></div></div></div></div> </div>
