<span id="ugc-review__chip--text_18-0" class="comp ugc-review__chip--text mntl-text-block">A keeper!</span></span></div>
<div id="ugc-review__text_9-0" class="comp ugc-review__text mntl-text-block">So I didn't follow the banana part I had five bananas that I used about medium size just so they didn't go to waste. Made about 2ish cups fully mashed down. But follow the recipe to the tea beyond that and it was fantastic!!! There's only one slice left and I only made it last night. I'm calling you bananarama bread though if that's okay 😬</div></div></div></div></div> </div>
